data.description: ** Assumable VA loan at 2.75%!  Ask the listing agent how!!!   (Rate to be verified with the seller)!!   Make this Triple Creek property your new home!  This bright and open floor plan will be perfect for all your family and entertaining needs!  This is a large corner lot with no backyard neighbor.  You will have ample privacy to enjoy your own space within a fully fenced in backyard lined with palm and pine trees on the border.  Enjoy the sunrise while sipping your morning coffee on your screened in front porch.  Grill and chill while relaxing on your screened lanai looking into your very private back yard.  The first floor has luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout.  All bedrooms are upstairs, with the Master separate from the other 3 bedrooms. Full size laundry room on the second floor also for convenience.  Triple Creek offers 2 clubhouses, elementary school, Goddard school, tennis, a very large pickle ball group, basketball, dog park, 2 playgrounds, 3 pools, miles of surrounding trails to walk or bike, and countless organized community activities.  This home is competitively priced to sell, owners are moving onto their next journey.  Please call to schedule a private showing.
